{"tid":2196468,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有中國學生證實被美取消簽證　曾就讀與解放軍聯繫大學","createTime":"2020-09-10T02:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T03:47:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b2477a1133b45c875b77c97edabfd3bd9f38dac9","tid":2196468,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T02:46:23.000Z","msg":"美國國務院證實，至今撤銷過千名中國公民的簽證，以阻止被認為對美國國家安全存在風險的學生及研究人員入境，強調不符合資格的研究生及學者，只是佔小部分。<br />\n<br />\n國土安全部代理部長沃爾夫在華盛頓演講時，指控中國濫用學生簽證，利用美國學術界，美方正阻止向某些與中國軍事融合戰略有聯繫的中國研究生和研究人員發出簽證，防止他們竊取或以其他方式挪用敏感研究成果。<br />\n<br />\n有中國學生證實，已經收到被取消簽證的通知，如果想去美國，必須重新申請簽證。有學生說，對美國政府的決定感到震驚，認為簽證被取消的唯一原因，與他曾經在中國就讀與解放軍有聯繫的大學有關。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548819-20200910.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548819-20200910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE05YX6KrfwXAFWAh9WWXcag%3D&h=fe50763e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548819-20200910.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=41c01153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548819-20200910.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3d109eeef76ff409183b5771ef61c61b2be6ddda","tid":2196468,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"中國人留美=反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fff37a79b1bfbe76efabaac8246b36d57f0c8a5","tid":2196468,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"點解要去美國讀？係咪想勾結外國勢力？"},{"pid":"bd38430f74eb05d0e85dbfd1a515421e11d081f4","tid":2196468,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T02:50:17.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smi